<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>I agree with @JP Richardson that Cheerio is best for scraping non-JS-heavy sites.
For JS-heavy sites, use <a href="http://casperjs.org/" rel="nofollow">Casper</a>. It provides great abstractions over Phantom and a promises-style API. They go over how to scrape in their docs: <a href="http://docs.casperjs.org/en/latest/quickstart.html" rel="nofollow">http://docs.casperjs.org/en/latest/quickstart.html</a>. </p>
    </div>
