<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>If you want to go for phantom, use node-phantom. I have a git hub repository using them together to generate pdf files from html if you want to have a look.
But i wouldn't go for phantom because it does more than what you usually want and cheerio is faster.</p>
    </div>
